Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.05,0:02:46.85,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Originally, make-up lessons during summer vacation are to take place during July.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.85,0:02:49.43,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Fact is, mine were scheduled near the end of July.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.33,0:02:55.61,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,But I, Kamijo Touma, still have to deal with make-up-make-up lessons as of August 20th, today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.61,0:02:58.44,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, it's because I skipped the make-up lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.44,0:03:05.37,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,The reason I use a vague term like "apparently" is because I lost my memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.37,0:03:08.07,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I lost all my memories prior to July 28th.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.84,0:03:15.75,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, right now, I feel like I have to "pay" out of nowhere for lessons I didn't skip myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.35,0:03:19.92,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Two thousand yen...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.12,0:03:35.27,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Such misfortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.41,0:03:37.43,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.43,0:03:39.74,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just stand there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.74,0:03:41.15,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of the way if you're not buying.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.80,0:03:48.52,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Tokiwadai Middle School's uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.52,0:03:49.99,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Who is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.99,0:03:52.07,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,And, what's with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.04,0:03:56.04,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,I-friggin'-have-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.41,0:03:58.50,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,a proper name called Misaka Mikoto, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.50,0:04:00.58,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Learn it already, you moron!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.34,0:04:09.28,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,So I do know her...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.61,0:04:13.12,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,That vending machine eats your money, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.12,0:04:14.85,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.98,0:04:16.69,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a cheating technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.69,0:04:19.81,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,A cheating technique that will make it spit out some juice without giving it any money.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.82,0:04:21.77,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Cheating technique?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.86,0:04:26.44,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Chaser!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.04,0:04:29.44,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Shorts...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.07,0:04:35.83,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,This vending machine is old, so the springs that hold the cans can be loosened easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.83,0:04:39.20,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Only problem is that you can't choose what's going to come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.90,0:04:41.41,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,And, what's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.41,0:04:44.72,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Do all the rich girls at Tokiwadai do these kind of things?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.72,0:04:46.75,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,That's pretty much how girls' schools are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.75,0:04:49.26,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be fantasizing about girls, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.32,0:04:56.47,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's thanks to you girls doing this all the time that the vending machine is broken, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.27,0:04:59.85,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,What are you getting all angry for?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.85,0:05:02.39,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like we've done any direct harm to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.98,0:05:04.77,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,...It ate your money?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.91,0:05:11.19,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,How much did it eat~?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.97,0:05:13.82,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,T-Two thousand yen...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.16,0:05:16.50,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Two thousand yen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.50,0:05:18.10,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you gave it a two thousand yen bill?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.10,0:05:20.17,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,So, you didn't drop coins in separately!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.17,0:05:22.62,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Heck, I don't blame the vending machine for eating it then!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.34,0:05:26.44,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let me get it back for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.44,0:05:27.54,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.41,0:05:29.76,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.78,0:05:37.22,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, so many cans are coming out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.22,0:05:39.36,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,A two thousand yen bill didn't come out,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.36,0:05:42.16,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm sure it spit out more than two thousand yen's worth of cans,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.16,0:05:43.19,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,so settle with this, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.83,0:05:46.15,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why are you running for your life?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.38,0:05:47.43,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.53,0:06:01.35,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.71,0:06:10.53,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of your happy denial mode and carry these juice cans already.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.53,0:06:12.46,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,These were yours to begin with, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.29,0:06:19.58,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like the second I accept these, I'll rapidly evolve from bystander to accomplice, and that scares me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.58,0:06:20.35,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Shit, it's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.97,0:06:26.56,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, if you're not gonna drink that Yoshinomi cider, I'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.21,0:06:32.33,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,What are you all nervous about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.33,0:06:37.79,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,You look like someone who ends up with stupid problems a lot because he thinks he's weak when he's really not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.79,0:06:40.74,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,You are one that has defeated\Nthe one and only Misaka Mikoto, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.72,0:06:46.47,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,At least take up the minimum responsibilities of a victor or else I'll have problems, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.47,0:06:47.83,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Defeated?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.83,0:06:49.52,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Me? Defeat her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.52,0:06:51.68,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,In what sport? What game?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.68,0:06:55.38,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever girls say the phrase "take responsibility",
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.38,0:06:58.22,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,there's always a terrible ring to it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.89,0:06:50.46,index alt,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Be proud you were able to defeat me,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.46,0:06:54.49,index alt,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,one of the seven Level 5 espers in this Academy City,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.49,0:06:57.84,index alt,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,to the level that I can say "Ah, I lost to this strong of a man".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.07,0:07:01.18,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you look like your wisdom teeth are hurting?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.46,0:07:04.07,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, just drink up, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.07,0:07:09.23,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,If I say this is a present from Mikoto-sensei,\Nthen underclassmen at my school faint on the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.23,0:07:10.72,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Faint?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.72,0:07:12.44,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,This ain't a shoujo manga, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.76,0:07:16.70,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,If it was just the level of shoujo manga,\Nthen I'd call that cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.17,0:07:20.41,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what I'm called at Tokiwadai?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.06,0:07:21.57,index alt,Kuroko,0000,0000,0000,,Oneesama?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.89,0:07:23.83,index,Kuroko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my gosh, Oneesama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:25.79,index,Kuroko,0000,0000,0000,,My, my, Oneesama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.79,0:07:28.54,index,Kuroko,0000,0000,0000,,Pretending that you went to make-up lessons...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.54,0:07:31.42,index,Kuroko,0000,0000,0000,,...when it was actually a pretext for this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.02,0:07:35.03,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Let me ask, just to be sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.03,0:07:36.92,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,What is this "pretext" you speak of?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.92,0:07:38.65,index,Kuroko,0000,0000,0000,,Is that not obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.65,0:07:41.34,index,Kuroko,0000,0000,0000,,To have a rendezvous with the gentleman there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.26,0:07:43.62,index,Kuroko,0000,0000,0000,,It is a pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.62,0:07:47.81,index,Kuroko,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Shirai Kuroko; I serve as Oneesama's herald.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.01,0:07:52.88,index,Kuroko,0000,0000,0000,,If you intend on "hitting on" Oneesama,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.88,0:07:55.74,index,Kuroko,0000,0000,0000,,please check with me first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.74,0:07:59.31,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,You... think...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.65,0:08:03.28,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,...this weirdo looks like my boyfriend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.64,0:08:08.59,index,Kuroko,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.08,0:08:11.75,index,Kuroko,0000,0000,0000,,Of all people, my Oneesama wouldn't be so low.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.75,0:08:17.55,index,Kuroko,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, please make sure you don't make any mistakes, okay, Oneesama?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.55,0:08:18.59,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,KUROKO!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.44,0:08:21.72,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Spread some weird rumor and I'll have your head, got that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.76,0:08:24.19,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Teleport...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.19,0:08:25.18,index,MISAKA,0000,0000,0000,,"Oneesama."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.18,0:08:26.71,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Not another?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.93,0:08:30.14,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Another one of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.14,0:08:31.77,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Misaka no. 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.36,0:08:36.32,index,MISAKA,0000,0000,0000,,"I am her 'sister'," said MISAKA immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.81,0:08:37.94,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.94,0:08:41.56,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,But your name should be Misaka something, yet you refer to yourself as Misaka, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.56,0:08:44.24,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Don't people usually use their first names?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.24,0:08:46.09,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be a big confusion within the family, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.09,0:08:50.22,index,MISAKA,0000,0000,0000,,"MISAKA's name is MISAKA," said MISAKA without delay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.22,0:08:54.21,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you wasting your time here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.88,0:09:00.38,index,MISAKA,0000,0000,0000,,"If you ask for why... I am here researching," said MISAKA with a clean answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.02,0:09:04.39,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh... researching...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.18,0:09:08.55,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sister, come over here for a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.55,0:09:11.99,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,There's a lot of things we need to talk about... a lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.99,0:09:15.57,index,MISAKA,0000,0000,0000,,"No, MISAKA has her own schedule," said MISAKA-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.57,0:09:16.77,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.50,0:09:19.53,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Just come.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.53,0:09:23.42,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be walking this way,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.42,0:09:26.49,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,you remember your own curfew, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.07,0:09:30.20,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,A rather complicated family, I guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.13,0:09:38.96,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,It's so hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.01,0:09:40.96,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,It's so cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.42,0:09:43.68,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,It's so heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.21,0:09:56.52,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,That was close, that was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.14,0:10:07.64,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait... a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.97,0:10:11.85,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.85,0:10:13.54,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell did I do to deserve-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.37,0:10:18.54,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.44,0:10:23.42,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you take your sister away somewhere earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.38,0:10:29.01,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, she was wearing shorts earlier, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.68,0:10:35.40,index,MISAKA,0000,0000,0000,,"I can lend you a hand if you need it," says MISAKA as she lets out a sigh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.10,0:10:40.44,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's the sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.44,0:10:42.86,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You really are the spitting image of Mikoto, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.67,0:10:47.53,index,MISAKA,0000,0000,0000,,"Mikoto?" as MISAKA asks back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.02,0:10:50.55,index,MISAKA,0000,0000,0000,,"Ah, you mean, Oneesama."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.55,0:10:53.54,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the hardcore military goggles?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.54,0:10:59.28,index,MISAKA,0000,0000,0000,,"MISAKA, unlike Oneesama, has no skill in tracking the flow of electrons and magnetic forces,"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.28,0:11:05.30,index,MISAKA,0000,0000,0000,,"and that's why a device to visualize them is needed," explained MISAKA cordially.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.97,0:11:06.94,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.66,0:11:11.47,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,But didn't your sister drag you away back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.42,0:11:18.10,index,MISAKA,0000,0000,0000,,"MISAKA came from that way," as she points to where.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.78,0:11:30.38,index,MISAKA,0000,0000,0000,,"Where shall I carry these juice cans to?" asks MISAKA while busying her hands and filling them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.38,0:11:34.16,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, I can carry these myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.87,0:11:41.16,index,MISAKA,0000,0000,0000,,"Where shall I carry these juice cans to?" MISAKA urges.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.25,0:11:44.69,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, it's okay, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.69,0:11:46.63,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason for you to carry them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.63,0:11:48.26,index,MISAKA,0000,0000,0000,,"Hurry up."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.97,0:11:49.97,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.24,0:12:01.51,index,Maika,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kamijo Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.12,0:12:05.76,index,Maika,0000,0000,0000,,My AC broke down, so I'm here for the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.76,0:12:09.07,index,Maika,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be making noise with my brother tonight, so bear with us, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.45,0:12:11.33,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuchimikado's here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.33,0:12:12.31,index,Maika,0000,0000,0000,,He's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.31,0:12:14.33,index,Maika,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea where he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.01,0:12:20.53,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,She is Maika, the step sister of Tsuchimikado, a classmate who lives next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.53,0:12:22.71,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, she goes to a maid school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.31,0:12:25.47,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Maid schools must be tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.47,0:12:27.51,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You guys have no summer vacation, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.17,0:12:33.18,index,Maika,0000,0000,0000,,"A true maid needs no vacation" is our school's motto.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.18,0:12:34.93,index,Maika,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Kamijo Touma.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.93,0:12:38.73,index,Maika,0000,0000,0000,,Are those the "spoils of war" from\Na raffle drawing you have in your hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.73,0:12:40.29,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,No, these have been paid for properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.29,0:12:44.06,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,A bit dirty of a job, but if you'd like one, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.86,0:12:46.27,index,Maika,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'll take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.11,0:12:53.41,index,Maika,0000,0000,0000,,Before I go, a tip on how to hide a runaway girl in your home:
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.41,0:12:56.29,index,Maika,0000,0000,0000,,Let the girl wander around in the city during the day...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.29,0:13:00.16,index,Maika,0000,0000,0000,,...and take her home at night;\Nthis "feeding" strategy is the easiest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.77,0:13:02.12,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.12,0:13:05.63,index,Maika,0000,0000,0000,,That Sister generates too much noise inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.11,0:13:15.83,index,MISAKA,0000,0000,0000,,"Do you have that kind of hobby?"\Nasks MISAKA in a slightly serious tone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.16,0:13:18.01,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.86,0:13:26.27,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What are those two doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.17,0:13:30.26,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.26,0:13:33.19,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Lost your keys and got locked out?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.19,0:13:34.70,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's Touma.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.70,0:13:36.06,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.06,0:13:39.37,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're with a strange girl again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.73,0:13:40.58,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.21,0:13:44.18,index,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps, that is his fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.59,0:13:49.00,index,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,He raises flags with other people and goes down their story routes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.50,0:13:53.63,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,And, what are you two doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.00,0:13:57.72,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Sphynx's got fleas all over him,\Nso we're getting them off of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.23,0:14:01.80,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Does that mean the room is full of fleas, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.80,0:14:04.69,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, so that's the reason I've felt itchy all over recently!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.69,0:14:07.27,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Touma.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.95,0:14:09.93,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What's... that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.93,0:14:12.33,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,It's a herb called sage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.33,0:14:17.49,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Put some heat on this\Nand it'll smoke out the fleas on Sphynx.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.49,0:14:19.19,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Smoke out...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.19,0:14:22.05,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to kill the cat or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.05,0:14:23.40,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Himegami!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.40,0:14:25.25,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What are you pulling out of your sleeves?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.34,0:14:28.71,index,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,A magical spray, that's the only thing I can say.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.69,0:14:31.71,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.71,0:14:35.80,index,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,All you need to do is spray at the insect.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.80,0:14:38.44,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,That's just a normal insecticide no matter how you look at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.44,0:14:40.97,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You plan to spray that directly on the cat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.50,0:14:43.97,index,MISAKA,0000,0000,0000,,"Concerning the way to deal with the cat..."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.94,0:14:50.35,index,MISAKA,0000,0000,0000,,"...in essence, you want to physically remove the fleas from the surface of the cat without using chemicals, correct?"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.35,0:14:52.44,index,MISAKA,0000,0000,0000,,says MISAKA to confirm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.59,0:14:56.24,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but... how are you going to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.24,0:14:59.41,index,MISAKA,0000,0000,0000,,"Like this," answers MISAKA immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.11,0:15:08.59,index,MISAKA,0000,0000,0000,,"With a particular frequency,\Nonly the insects are killed," reports MISAKA.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.59,0:15:16.88,index,MISAKA,0000,0000,0000,,"For fleas inside your room, it is best to use the fog-type insecticide," advises MISAKA.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.23,0:15:19.54,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.85,0:15:25.27,index,MISAKA,0000,0000,0000,,"Well then, if that is all..."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.13,0:15:39.66,index,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx96}Regarding the mandatory requirement for the re-establishing of ESP card experimentation in the United States in 1992,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.15,0:15:43.07,index,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,the material for the card was changed to ABS resin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.07,0:15:46.71,index,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,This is a trick to handle the problem of being able to tell the type of card...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.71,0:15:49.80,index,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,...from the finger oil making up the fingerprints on the back of the card and...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.80,0:15:53.13,index,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you listening, Kamijo-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.08,0:15:59.88,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I am, but it's not like I can gain power from listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.35,0:16:02.85,index,blue hair,0000,0000,0000,,Kami-yan's a Level 0 after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.85,0:16:05.60,index,blonde,0000,0000,0000,,What can't increase won't increase.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.60,0:16:10.94,index,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,But, but, you can't stop improving something you could just because you think you have no power and give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.55,0:16:17.63,index,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,No. 3 in the Academy City, Tokiwadai Middle School's\NMisaka-san was really a Level 1,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.63,0:16:21.99,index,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,and she worked really, really hard to reach Level 5 now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.33,0:16:24.33,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,No. 3? Her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.30,0:16:28.08,index,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,Kamijo-chan, you know Misaka-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.01,0:16:31.07,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,No, not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.29,0:16:46.30,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.71,0:16:48.68,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You headed home after make-up lessons, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.80,0:16:57.44,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.42,0:17:05.03,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like that blimp very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.20,0:17:07.37,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.31,0:17:12.63,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Because humans are abiding by the policies set by machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.63,0:17:13.74,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Machines?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.74,0:17:16.47,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, what was it... umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.47,0:17:19.35,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,"Tree Diagram" or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.35,0:17:26.67,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Tree Diagram - the most powerful supercomputer in the world, installed inside Orihime 1,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.67,0:17:31.14,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,the artificial satellite the Academy City launched using "weather data processing" as a cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.87,0:17:37.98,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,That's what they say, but does something as extravagant as that really exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.48,0:17:39.39,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.52,0:17:42.87,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.87,0:17:45.01,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you do that all of a sudden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.01,0:17:48.09,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh, I've become a bit of a poet now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.83,0:17:51.70,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.16,0:17:54.46,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,I'm this way, bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.19,0:18:13.77,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,That's Mikoto, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.64,0:18:18.31,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's her sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.31,0:18:21.73,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I really can't tell the difference without the goggles.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.14,0:18:28.16,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, thanks for the juice and fleas yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.16,0:18:33.08,index,MISAKA,0000,0000,0000,,"Your compliments were not\Nmy objectives," answers MISAKA.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.97,0:18:39.04,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What, you're not going to feed it that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.43,0:18:46.91,index,MISAKA,0000,0000,0000,,"It is probably impossible for MISAKA to feed this to the cat," concludes MISAKA.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.91,0:18:53.05,index,MISAKA,0000,0000,0000,,"MISAKA possesses a very critical defect," as MISAKA gives additional explanations.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.05,0:18:53.77,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Defect?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.51,0:18:59.80,index,MISAKA,0000,0000,0000,,"MISAKA's body passively generates\Na weak magnetic field," explains MISAKA.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.80,0:19:05.51,index,MISAKA,0000,0000,0000,,"Its magnitude isn't one a human body can detect, but that is not the case for other animals."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.95,0:19:12.83,index,MISAKA,0000,0000,0000,,"At this rate, it is to fear that this cat will be taken away to an animal shelter," indicates MISAKA.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.83,0:19:15.20,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You're... right... but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.61,0:19:22.13,index,MISAKA,0000,0000,0000,,"Do you know how animals taken to\Nan animal shelter are treated?" presses MISAKA.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.73,0:19:32.16,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you picked it up, at least give it a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.20,0:19:34.10,index,MISAKA,0000,0000,0000,,"Dog."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.89,0:19:38.73,index,MISAKA,0000,0000,0000,,"This black cat will be called 'Dog'," declares MISAKA.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.59,0:19:42.52,index,MISAKA,0000,0000,0000,,"A cat, yet 'Dog'... hehe..."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.53,0:19:48.36,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,No, let's be serious... let's give it one that's more majestic or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.47,0:19:53.49,index,MISAKA,0000,0000,0000,,"Then, 'Tokugawa Ieyasu'," as MISAKA changes her mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.49,0:19:55.44,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,That's too majestic, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.44,0:19:57.33,index,MISAKA,0000,0000,0000,,"Schrödinger, then."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.74,0:20:00.61,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,That name is taboo for cats.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.95,0:20:05.09,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be out right away, so wait here for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.58,0:20:11.78,index,MISAKA,0000,0000,0000,,"Do you want reference books for taking care of cats?" says MISAKA to get confirmation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.78,0:20:13.90,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,More like knowledge and not the books themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.90,0:20:15.21,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You saw them, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.21,0:20:17.68,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,The Sister clothing and the shrine maiden clothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.28,0:20:21.45,index,MISAKA,0000,0000,0000,,"I would like to remind you, just in case,"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.45,0:20:29.13,index,MISAKA,0000,0000,0000,,"but mistreating the lives of cats is a crime under the Animal Protection Act," warns MISAKA.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.13,0:20:31.42,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What, are you angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.51,0:20:34.27,index,MISAKA,0000,0000,0000,,"I am not angry."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.27,0:20:39.05,index,MISAKA,0000,0000,0000,,"I am saying that just because you weren't directly involved in such mistreatment does not mean you are off the hook,"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.05,0:20:41.36,index,MISAKA,0000,0000,0000,,advises MISAKA.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.36,0:20:42.29,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,My bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.06,0:20:49.46,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is it okay for me to bring a cat into a bookstore?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.50,0:20:57.31,index,MISAKA,0000,0000,0000,,"This may sound quite mundane, but please refrain from letting us take care of it, thank you," as MISAKA-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.50,0:21:04.85,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You said cats don't like you because of your magnetic field?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.85,0:21:08.78,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Then overcome that barrier, and true friendship is born.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.20,0:21:19.04,index,MISAKA,0000,0000,0000,,"Gosh... with what kind of mentality can someone throw a cat like that?" utters MISAKA to herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.50,0:21:47.81,index,Accel.,0000,0000,0000,,Now, question.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.81,0:21:53.65,index,Accel.,0000,0000,0000,,Who comes to mind when they ask who the strongest Level 5 in this Academy City is?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.17,0:23:27.72,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Massacres that have taken place in the name of "experimentation".
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.72,0:23:29.83,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Those targets are called "Sisters".
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.05,0:23:33.04,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, MISAKA, how much do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.77,0:23:35.50,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, "Sisters".
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.50,0:23:37.44,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,When science and magic cross paths,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.44,0:23:38.50,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,this epic will begin!
